command.toneko.xp: §aThe xp between neko %s §a and you is %s-nya
command.toneko.help:
§b/toneko help:
§a/toneko help §bI am sure you know what this command can do.
§a/toneko player <player> §bBe a neko's owner
§a/toneko aliases <neko> add or remove <alias> §bAdd a alias to neko（If neko say the word,the word will become 'owner'）
§a/toneko block <neko> add or remove <blocked word> <replacement> word or all §bAdd a blocked word（the blocked word will replace with replacement)
command.toneko.noPermission: §aThat's sad because you have no permission to do this command
command.tonekoadmin.help:
§b/tonekoadmin help:
§a/tonekoadmin help §bget help
§a/tonekoadmin set <player> §bSet player to neko or unset
§a/tonekoadmin reload §bReload the config and language
command.neko.help:
§b/neko getHelp(These commands only for neko):
§a/neko jump §bJump higher!
§a/neko vision §bDo you want to see clearly as a neko at night?
§a/neko speed §bToo quickly(>_<)
§a/neko lie §bLie down and rest for a while
§a/neko nickname <nickname> §bSet a cute nickname
§a/neko level §bShow your neko level
§a/neko lore <lore> §bSet a cute lore for your item in hand.

message.toneko.crystal_neko.who.1: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bHmm... This name is a little hard to remember...
message.toneko.crystal_neko.who.2: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bBut it doesn't matter，you don't have to call me full name... Call me any alias if you like.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.who.5: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bBut... I am so happy that you can play it.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.who.6: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bDo you want to listen to me saying other things? I am happy to say to you!
message.toneko.crystal_neko.about_mod.0: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §btoNeko... At first, it was a plugin. I just made it for fun.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.about_mod.1: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bThen... I made a vid and publish on BiliBili(A Chinese video website)
message.toneko.crystal_neko.about_mod.2: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bBut... To my surprise, it getting a little popular.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.about_mod.4: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bThen... I made up my mind. I decided to continue to develop.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.about_mod.5: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bBut why it been a mod... I have something to say.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.about_mod.6: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bBecause the user of plugin is not so many, so I made Mod version.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.about_mod.7: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bAs I expected, the mod version is more popular than plugin version.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.about_mod.8: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bHum... In June,2024, I even rewrite it.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.about_mod.9: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bRewrite... You maybe know the workload of it.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.about_mod.10: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bBut... For future develop, I still decided to do it.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.about_mod.11: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bCome to think of it... toNeko has also celebrated its first anniversary...
message.toneko.crystal_neko.about_mod.12: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bI really didn't expect that I could last this long.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.about_mod.15: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bThanks for listening I say this store.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.plans.0: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bAbout the update plan of this mod...
message.toneko.crystal_neko.plans.3: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bBasically... I just do whatever I think is fun.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.plans.4: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bIt is constantly updated with the themes of "Neko" and "Kawai"...
message.toneko.crystal_neko.plans.5: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bSo... As you can see... The updates are so scattered
message.toneko.crystal_neko.plans.6: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bEmm... Now main update is on Fabric.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.plans.7: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bAlthough NeoForge maybe update, but it slower than Fabric version...
message.toneko.crystal_neko.plans.8: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bBecause... I don't have so many time...
message.toneko.crystal_neko.plans.9: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bAnd Bukkit.... I have no time to do it
message.toneko.crystal_neko.plans.10: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bSo maybe... I will make the Fabric version only in future.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.plans.11: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bNow main work is make neko NPC.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.plans.12: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bBecause there is so less content in single-player mode
message.toneko.crystal_neko.plans.13: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bAt least with the neko, the single-player mode can also experience a lot of content.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.plans.15: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bIf you have any good ideas, you can tell me on github-nya.
§dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bYou... You want to mate with me?
message.toneko.crystal_neko.nya_tried.2: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §cIf you do this again, I... I will be angry!
